 岛 遇 缺 遥 摇 兔 逸 免 晚\u003cbr /\u003e象 像 马 妈 吗 骂 验 骑 虎 虑 虚 鹿 熊 能 寅 演 辰 晨 关 送 联 鬼 魔 龙 袭\u003cbr /\u003e那 哪 两 俩 满 县 悬 窗 电 掩 丑 扭 黄 横 赤 亦 弯 湾 恋 变 卑 牌 套 曰 属\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003c/div\u003eThat is the first 1500 Chinese characters that Heisig proposes we remember. That is a lot of Chinese characters to take in, in one go. Having done some quick maths, if I learn 15 a day from now until my birthday on January 20th 2010. I should be able to complete the first 1500 hanzi thanks to Heisig and you guys for inspiring me.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eHere are the hanzi all printed out and stuck up in my room. :D Whilst at the moment they are achieving not a lot by being there. By my 22nd birthday I hope to be able to understand them all.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003ca onblur\u003d\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href\u003d\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_ia4h1rKanAQ/StOQaMD6AcI/AAAAAAAAA58/BmJ9hvrzdZQ/s1600-h/hanzi+heisig+method.JPG\"\u003e\u003cimg style\u003d\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 400px; height: 300px;\" src\u003d\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_ia4h1rKanAQ/StOQaMD6AcI/AAAAAAAAA58/BmJ9hvrzdZQ/s400/hanzi+heisig+method.JPG\" alt\u003d\"\" id\u003d\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5391811958481224130\" border\u003d\"0\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003ca onblur\u003d\"try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}\" href\u003d\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_ia4h1rKanAQ/StOXO145bFI/AAAAAAAAA6E/7QI462kbJbM/s1600-h/hanzi+wall+poster.JPG\"\u003e\u003cimg style\u003d\"margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 400px; height: 300px;\" src\u003d\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_ia4h1rKanAQ/StOXO145bFI/AAAAAAAAA6E/7QI462kbJbM/s400/hanzi+wall+poster.JPG\" alt\u003d\"\" id\u003d\"BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5391819460132301906\" border\u003d\"0\" /\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSo here is to Heisig. And here is to to a journey of learning m